data.description: This beautiful Medallion-built property in Cross Creek is the perfect 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom to make yours! Not only is Cross Creek a highly desirable community to live in with pedestrian friendly sidewalks everywhere, pool, waterslide, splash-pad, playground, and dog park, this "Harbour" model has several upgrades that elevate and modernize the home. Porcelain tile and high ceilings throughout, tray ceiling in the living room, and the open floor plan creates a contemporary palate to maximize your living space and seating for larger gatherings. The kitchen features quartz countertops, matte finished cabinetry, and a brick backsplash giving the kitchen a sleek setting for cooking and mealtimes. Relax on the screened-in lanai and enjoy the open backyard with room for a pool, of course! This home is perfectly located to access all that St. Pete has to offer with a 30 minute drive to the North; head south for 30 minutes and you'll hit University Parkway which offers endless dining and shopping options in Sarasota. Another 30 minutes West, and you can walk to sugary sands of Anna Maria Island. Come see this home for yourself, your ideal Florida lifestyle awaits you! MOTIVATED SELLERS; schedule a showing today !
